data.description: GREAT FAMILY HOME 3 bedrooms 2 baths with an awesome floor plan. Large living room & dining room combination with wood floors.  Great kitchen layout with granite countertops, breakfast bar & ceramic flooring. Lots of cabinets space and stainless appliances with gas range. Features a great master bed & bath area with his/hers closets, garden tub with large separate shower. Corner lot with two driveways - one to the front garage and the other to the side of the home. Fenced in yard along with separate storage.
